[I] A simple editor for simple needs

[T] This editor pays homage to the classic MS-DOS Editor, but with a modern
[T] interface and input controls similar to VS Code. The goal is to provide an
[T] accessible editor that even users largely unfamiliar with terminals can
[T] easily use.

